name: TechCrunch
text:
ICYMI: You likely haven't heard of BlueKai, but it tracks millions of people across the web, collecting browsing data to infer your interests and tastes to serve you targeted ads. 

Thanks to an unprotected server, that data spilled online.

Our exclusive: https://t.co/VWOZLjdlSm

text:
